{"tid":1612214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請不要再破壞香港","createTime":"2019-10-02T07:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T08:05:03.000Z","uid":135784,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ee07fddc07eff0c743db83d0419b014c8adbec2d","tid":1612214,"uid":135784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:36:43.000Z","msg":"屌你老母就要搞撚死呢個港共下既香港<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>If we burn, you burn with us</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n好而家請大家一齊討論下點實行<br />\n<br />\n我睇咗好多位手足既pose之後 建議行<span style=\"color: red;\">小隊制</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 5-6人一個小組 (必須肯定係可靠隊友 會救人果種）<br />\n<br />\n2. 大原則hit and run 小隊咁行動最緊要係靈活<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<br />\n<br />\n1. 點搵隊友<br />\n<br />\n2. 攻擊對象?如果對住美心用火魔法 入面有人咁點<br />\n<br />\n3. 點避天眼? 係屋企出嚟幾時要換裝 Hit完之後幾時再換番普通衫"},{"pid":"f35a684218f79b438e7c044878ba4a1469c18c97","tid":1612214,"uid":135784,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:37:03.000Z","msg":"好想打遊擊"},{"pid":"270a998c3abc406e5d289aa855d06878d0cb69bd","tid":1612214,"uid":135784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:37:22.000Z","msg":"正面衝突冇意思"},{"pid":"f72dc7c5d433245895227bab422203f5d5740e4f","tid":1612214,"uid":135784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:37:41.000Z","msg":"只會令更多手足受傷 被捕"},{"pid":"34cc1c0fe4650dc5f665edd0e0bdc8617a3d318a","tid":1612214,"uid":135784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:37:58.000Z","msg":"遊擊大前題 不被捕 不流血"},{"pid":"0dae328d40c36ab2c137d368396bced05394c574","tid":1612214,"uid":135784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:38:12.000Z","msg":"隊友質素好重要"},{"pid":"2a0c08e836ba60ba60c244b6557e3d2f05c75103","tid":1612214,"uid":135784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:38:53.000Z","msg":"其實最諗唔到係點搞第三點 周圍都係cam"},{"pid":"8d8609d086579630d4c71c7da6a3b32e73bf2dee","tid":1612214,"uid":135784,"like